data.description: Don't Miss this Large Home Close to downtown Elberton.  Tons of unique features.  Main floor consists of the open living area with massive picture window with awesome views of the private backyard.  Kitchen with large island, lots of cabinets with plenty of storage, double pantry closets.    Formal dining area. 1st Master on Main and also a 2nd bedroom on the main floor.  Large Laundry upstairs with access from the 2nd master bedroom. 3 additional bedrooms upstairs and an open area for office space, playroom etc.  Beautiful private backyard with large deck for family entertainment.
